I calculated the power requirements for 510 WS2812B LEDs. At 60mA per LED, the total is around 30.6A at 5V. I researched how to safely power large LED installations such as this and learned about voltage drop, power injection, and wire gauge. I also looked at different 5V power supplies that fit the budget.

